    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072660/extras/9ab220d9c8913f400d27c279138d1164.avif?t=1759902493\" width=616 height=200 /></span><strong>Will you stay close to safety and see where the journey leads, or will you venture further to find answers and risk it all?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ex Nihilo is a non-linear, narrative driven sci-fi adventure with a touch of cosmic horror.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You awaken in a pod. You have been taken. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But by whom? And where are you headed?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072660/extras/159ad7ccbd976ba6d4097d92ce5ca82a.poster.avif?t=1759902493\" width=616 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072660/extras/159ad7ccbd976ba6d4097d92ce5ca82a.webm?t=1759902493\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072660/extras/159ad7ccbd976ba6d4097d92ce5ca82a.mp4?t=1759902493\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>On your journey through an interconnected world, time is limited. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You have just ten days to escape before reaching your final destination.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But stray from your pod for too long, and strange beings begin to appear…</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>And they have their eye on you.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072660/extras/e6875c4b50f80f812e06ddbca19c7d9f.poster.avif?t=1759902493\" width=616 height=241 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072660/extras/e6875c4b50f80f812e06ddbca19c7d9f.webm?t=1759902493\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Squint your eyes to avoid detection and make your way back to safety.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Reawaken, to find yourself one day further from home, with less time to escape …</p>",
